HDO BOX - Movies app for Android, iOS (ios not included), and TV. (AD-FREE)
Best Application for watching movies on any device.

Please Read All!

When updating: You need to update from this GitHub, not from the app.. 

Download:
----

AD-Free on this GitHub..

Ad-free features: no ads!, faster load times, no waiting, and free content for all!

Installation: If you have HDO Box already on the device, clear data, remove it (uninstall), then install this one, and the mod should be in place and work.. 

We recommend using a DNS (not the same exactly to a VPN) to spead up server's load time, like personaldnsfilter from the Play Store, Fdroid or Github (will also help block ads, if this is not up to date)..

